txt.en: 'We have been discussing the situation in Lamedon. How have you found it?'
'I heard that raiders from the shore have come up the rivers.'
'Is it true that corsair raiders have come up the rivers?'
'Lamedon is a land of fields and farmers. We are unprepared for battle!'
'Prince Imrahil rode for Minas Tirith. His daughter rules now in Dol Amroth.'
